    border-collapse: collapse;
    width: 90%;
}}
th, td {{
    border: 1px solid black;
    padding: 8px;
    text-align: center;
}}
th {{
    background-color: #f2f2f2;
}}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<h1>üçΩÔ∏è Food Wastage Analysis Dashboard</h1>

<h2>üìã Dataset</h2>
{df.to_html(index=False)}

<h2>üìä Statistical Summary</h2>
{summary.to_html()}

<h2>üìå Key Insights</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Rice has the highest wastage due to overproduction</li>
    <li>Spoilage is the most common wastage reason</li>
    <li>Chennai and Coimbatore contribute maximum wastage</li>
</ul>

<h2>üéØ Conclusion</h2>
<p>
Food wastage can be reduced by better inventory planning,
improved storage facilities, and food donation programs.
</p>

</body>
</html>
""")
